It's a small Dominican spot that serves food throughout the day. The food itself is great but I can't say the same about the service. There have been times when I've ordered food for pickup 30-45 minutes beforehand and it's still not ready when I arrive. There have been others times when I've ordered food for delivery and it took longer than it should have.  What ultimately stopped me from ordering from this place was that my mom got a stomach virus after eating food from here earlier this year. It's a shame because the food isn't bad at all.
